780
01:26:32,688 --> 01:26:33,887
Roy?

781
01:26:33,889 --> 01:26:35,455
Edward.

782
01:26:35,457 --> 01:26:37,124
Chào Flora. Chị thế nào?

783
01:26:37,126 --> 01:26:39,660
À, rất vui vì gặp lại anh,
Edward

784
01:26:39,662 --> 01:26:41,161
